 Quilldart and Galvatron stopped at the scene. Galvatron sent out a comm to 
Megatron. "There can only be one true Megatron on this planet. Come let us 
settle this decepticon style. Fight me now!" He sent shadow star the signal.

Quilldart transformed into robot mode. He sent a comm to the non tripred 
forces there. "We are here to fight the tripreds alone." He shot off his horn 
 missles at the tripred base.

--part1_1a2.7b1c69c.2a9ce907_boundary
